

To run the spike:

./prepare.sh
./build-image.sh
./run-test.sh


If you're hacking snapd:

./build-snapd.sh
./build-image.sh
./run-test.sh




Approx. run times (qemu running on AMD R7 2700 w/ spinning disk):

- from boot to version chooser: 40s
- install time: approx. 30s
- installed system to console-conf: 5min30s <- slooow

